description: The Pest Experts skill will the top tips on the prevention of common household pests such as mice, cockroaches, and flies. From tips on cleaning up common feeding sites to the times of day to avoid mosquitoes, these tips will help tackle common pests.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Rentokil Experts how to get rid of ants.
Ask Rentokil Experts, "how do I prevent mice?"
Ask Rentokil Experts how to treat cockroaches.
name: Rentokil Pest Experts
shortDescription: Ask the Pest Experts for tips on the prevention of common household pests such as mice, cockroaches, and flies.
